longBusinessSummary: Phoenix Biotech Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. The company intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. It engages in identifying and acquiring a business that focuses on the healthcare or healthcare related industries in the United States and Europe. Phoenix Biotech Acquisition Corp. was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Oakland, California.
